nodes.text: The Kedorzhan Bar was a bar located on Taris. It was also referred to as the Underworld Cantina of Taris. Sometime during the Mandalorian Wars, the bar was visited by Zayne Carrick and Marn Hierogryph on the run from Zayne's master, Lucien Draay. The bar was mainly visited by Kedorzhans to have a couple of drinks after long shifts in the mines.
